author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
You many have heard me mention Danny Sapko recently as part of the Reactor Community here on YouTube. But he's also a musician in his own right. His YouTube Channel is a great watch for many reasons - as I hope you'll see from our chat. 
***Please note - apologies for some of the sound quality on Danny - we had some trouble with the line******

To see more from Danny: https://www.youtube.com/@UCPVjQ58A0BujzVMEmFCJ3hA 

To watch Becky Baldwin's cover of Seek and Destroy: https://youtu.be/cUG8G1GaNis?si=Qalknn0Cgb-suG0T

To come and see Justin Hawkins Rides Again LIVE across the UK, find tickets here: 
https://www.aegpresents.co.uk/event/justin-hawkins-rides-again/

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

The latest Darkness album "Dreams On Toast" is here: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/

Get a Justin Hawkins Rides Again T-Shirt & Hoodie here: https://thejawsofvictory
